law.text:
A voter registration volunteer or any individual assisting another individual to register to vote may not:
copy or collect the following information contained on a voter registration application:
Maryland driver's license number;
Maryland identification number;
Social Security number; or
other information from a voter registration application that is protected from public disclosure;
use any voter registration information for a purpose inconsistent with § 3-507 of this title; and
receive any form of compensation, including bonuses, that is based on the number of voter registration applications collected.
